    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……今日は間に合ったな。お疲れ様です、莉央さん\nMVの撮影はもうすぐですよね。準備は出来てますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whew… I made it on time today. Good work‚ Rio-san.\nThe MV shoot is coming up soon‚ right? Are you ready?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.5666254044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "当然じゃない。そういう{user}さんは\n今日の撮影にはギリギリ間に合ったみたいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. And you‚ {user}-san—\nIt seems you barely made it in time for today’s shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2533176002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.5075778008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、葵のMV撮影の日には、前の仕事が押して\n遅刻したって聞いたわよ、売れっ子マネージャーさん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I heard you were late on Aoi’s MV shoot day‚\nbecause your previous job ran long‚ Mr. Popular Manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9923397701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirまでBIG4になったから大忙しですよ\nそういう莉央さんも、ここしばらく忙しかったでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re super busy now that LizNoir made it into the BIG4.\nYou’ve been pretty busy yourself lately‚ haven’t you‚ Rio-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.8666671117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.8508912405
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。あの後すぐ海外ツアーに行って、帰国早々\n新曲のレコーディングがあって、今日はMV撮影でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Right after that‚ we went on an overseas tour‚ and as soon as we got back‚\nwe had recording for the new song‚ and today is the MV shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0087832452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "目指していたBIG4にやっとなれた……って\n感慨にふける暇さえなかったわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We finally achieved our goal of making it into the BIG4… but\nI haven’t even had time to feel emotional about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.8087832452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.5340888341
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "でも新曲のレコーディングとMV撮影が急に入ったのは\nそもそも莉央さん達が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the reason the recording and MV shoot were suddenly scheduled is\nbecause you all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.6827154067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるわよ。『Grab the BIG4』で\n私達が披露する予定のない新曲をやったせいなんでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know. During “Grab the BIG4‚”\nwe performed a new song that wasn’t planned.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.402332147,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}